New Records: Virat Kohli scored 95 runs, the highest score in the match
Mohammed Shami took a five-wicket haul
The match was held at an altitude of 1457 meters in Dharamsala
Key Match Events: Fog delayed the match during the 16th over
Play resumed after the fog cleared
India won the match to maintain their unbeaten World Cup record
Miscellaneous Highlights: The venue's high altitude contributed to the fog conditions
The match was part of the ICC Men's Cricket World Cup 2023
